---
title: Presto Pesto Pea and Chicken Penne with Spinach and Roasted Tomatoes
description: Hey presto! This speedy Presto Pesto Pea and Chicken Penne is ready in under 25 minutes. Peas, roasted tomatoes and green veg make for an elevated version of classic pesto pasta.
